{"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)startServerCommunication","symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","title":"startServerCommunication","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"startServerCommunication","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"startServerCommunication","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"startServerCommunication","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Starts or resumes communication with Pushwoosh servers. This allows the SDK to send and receive","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"data including device registration, tags, push tokens, and analytics."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Call this method after the user has consented to data collection, or to re-enable"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"communication after it was previously stopped.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Example","type":"heading","anchor":"Example","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Enable communication after GDPR consent:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["class ConsentManager {","","    func handleUserConsent(accepted: Bool) {","        if accepted {","            \/\/ User accepted data collection","            Pushwoosh.configure.startServerCommunication()","","            \/\/ Register for push after consent","            Pushwoosh.configure.registerForPushNotifications()","","            \/\/ Sync any pending user data","            syncPendingUserData()","","            Logger.info(\"User consented - Pushwoosh communication enabled\")","        } else {","            \/\/ User declined - disable communication","            Pushwoosh.configure.stopServerCommunication()","            Logger.info(\"User declined - Pushwoosh communication disabled\")","        }","","        UserDefaults.standard.set(accepted, forKey: \"gdprConsent\")","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"called "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"stopServerCommunication"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/startServerCommunication"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/startservercommunication"]}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"text":"Enables communication with Pushwoosh servers.","type":"text"}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"title":"PushwooshCore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","type":"topic","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/startServerCommunication":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/startServerCommunication","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"startServerCommunication","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","title":"startServerCommunication","kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"startServerCommunication"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Enables communication with Pushwoosh servers.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/startservercommunication"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"abstract":[],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"PWConfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"}}}